That’s a wrap for this year’s Be a Hero 5K with @centersinatra Grateful to have another opportunity to bring awareness to child abuse prevention. #FightChildAbuse #BSCCPartner #sponsored

I got to met this amazing human at @centersinatra  He asked me about training & how to get better. So I told him to run the 5K with me. Now most people know that I don’t run but I was motivated by him to show that mindset is everything. One step at a time & it’s not about how you start but about how you finish. We ended making it to the final stretch & told him we have to sprint across the finish line ending with a time of 25 mins & 16 secs. Never have either one of us done a 5K so I’d say that is a great first time. But more importantly we pushed through the pain & proved that he can do anything you set your mind too. Lead By Example! #FightChildAbuse #BSCCPartner

There is a very big difference between FEAR & DANGER. Coaching kids & adults to realize that most of us live in FEAR when it comes to making things happen.FEAR -  If you are scared to do something, that’s in our minds. DANGER - If what you are doing can get your seriously injured without the proper training or experience. Small examples but it’s examples I get to prove in really time. The idea is to create individual who have dreams & goals to attack them without the FEAR of failure or what other people think about them.
